# Insight Blog — Frontend Architecture & Conventions

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 16 (App Router) with React 18
- **Language:** JavaScript (with JSDoc for critical types)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 3.3 + CSS custom properties (`:root` vars)
- **Data Fetching:** SWR / useSWRInfinite (client), native `fetch` (server)
- **HTTP Client:** Axios (2 instances: public + private/auth)
- **i18n:** next-intl (locales: `vi`, `en`)
- **Rich Text:** TipTap (see `.cursor/rules/editor-rule.mdc`)
- **Animations:** Framer Motion 11
- **Icons:** @phosphor-icons/react (primary), react-icons (legacy — migrate away)
- **Infinite Scroll:** react-infinite-scroll-component

