## Naming Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|-----------|---------|
| Components | PascalCase | `PostList`, `BasePostItem` |
| Hooks | camelCase with `use` prefix | `useInfinitePosts`, `useAuth` |
| Service functions | camelCase verb-first | `getPosts`, `createPost`, `fetchUserPosts` |
| Utils | camelCase | `renderPostContent`, `combineClasses` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `USER_ROLES`, `PAGE_SIZE` |
| CSS variables | kebab-case with `--` prefix | `--text-muted`, `--bg-surface` |
| Files | PascalCase for components, camelCase for hooks/utils/services | `PostList.js`, `useAuth.js`, `postService.js` |

### Service function naming
- `get*` — fetch single/paginated public data
- `fetch*` — fetch data (legacy, prefer `get*` for new code)
- `create*` — POST new resource
- `update*` — PUT/PATCH existing resource
- `delete*` — DELETE resource

