## Backend API Response Format

Backend (Go) returns responses in this format:
```json
{
  "data": [...],          // Array of items (or single object)
  "total_count": 100,     // Total items for pagination
  "next_cursor": "abc"    // For cursor-based pagination (comments/replies)
}
```

Single resource:
```json
{
  "data": { "post": { ... } }
}
```

- Backend uses `snake_case` field names
- Frontend services transform to `camelCase` before returning
